Que 17. Write a program to print product of only even
elements of an array.
Input : arr = {1, 2, 3, 4, 5}
Output: product = 8

public static void q17(int[]arr)
	{
		int product = 1;
		for(int i: arr)
		{
			if(i%2==0)
			{
				product = product*i;
				
			}
		}
		System.out.println(product);
	}


Que 18. Write a program to print product of only odd
elements of an array.
Input : arr = {1, 2, 3, 4, 5}
Output: product = 15
public static void q18(int[]arr)
	{
		int product =1;
		for(int i:arr)
		{
			if(i%2!=0)
			{
				product = product*i;
			}
		}
		System.out.println(product);
	}
